text = "HOW TO PLAY:

OBJECTIVE:
- You must explore the dungeon facing monsters, learning and crafting alchemic recipes along the way. Defeat the level's boss to progress to the next one.

CONTROLS:
- Use the mouse to drag and drop reagents from your hand to your crafting grid and click the combine button to attempt to combine the reagents into a recipe.
- You can click the \"Recipes\" button (shortcut: Tab) to open your recipe list, clicking a recipe in this list shows the reagents you have to place in your grid. While reagents are being shown in the grid in this way, you can click the corresponding reagent in your hand with the right mouse button to send it to the correct position automatically (you can also right click any reagent just to quick place it into the grid).
- When you can't or don't want to use any further reagents, click the \"End Turn\" button and the enemies will take their actions according to their intents shown above them.

TIPS:
- After combining the same recipe several times you master it, allowing you to favorite it to quickly combine it if you have the necessary reagents."
